workouts.title: Workout
workouts.introText:
You've put a lot of foundational work into your back, now let's take it even further.


Lock in your form on the new moves with the tutorial before you start.

groups.title: Warm-up
groups.summary: Switch on your back muscles, ready for action.

groups.title: Round 1
groups.summary: Big reps for your upper back and lats.

groups.title: Round 2
groups.summary: Lock in good form to build strength and posture.

groups.title: Round 3
groups.summary: A change in grip will maximize muscle activation.

groups.title: Round 4
groups.summary: Inverted rows add power to your posture, while shrugs will supercharge your size. Huge reps here, so stay focused.
